Raz mkstat
Call TEXTE(1427,GBOUT1) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_FCY(zc) From W1OBI1
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_FCY(zc) From W1OBI1
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_FCY(zc) From W1OBI1
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_FCY(zc) From W1OBI1
Gosub _AFF
